item.title: CVE-2023-34366|2024-09-12T18:05:25.878Z -- ichitaro%202023 -- ichitaro%202023
item.description: A use-after-free vulnerability exists in the Figure stream parsing functionality of Ichitaro 2023 1.0.1.59372. A specially crafted document can cause memory corruption, resulting in arbitrary code execution. Victim would need to open a malicious file to trigger this vulnerability.
